               <msContents>
                  <summary>Anonymous commentary on prayers, with additional quoted commentaries</summary>
                  <msItem>
                     <title type="desc">Commentary on the tefillot</title>
                     <title type="desc" xml:lang="he">פרוש התפלות</title>
                     <title type="desc" xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Perush ha-tefillot</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="he">Hebrew</textLang>
                     <note>This commentary contains quoted sections of other commentaries:
                        1: Fols. <locus from="101r" to="111r">101r-111r</locus> and <locus from="114r" to="142v">114r-142v</locus>, commentary by <persName key="person_59876084">Joseph Kara</persName>.
                        2: Fols. <locus from="111r" to="114r">111r-114r</locus>, parts of a commentary on New Year liturgy by <persName key="person_75197037">Eliezer ben Nathan of Mainz</persName>.
                        3: Fols. <locus from="114v" to="160r">114v-160r</locus>, commentary on piyyutim by <persName key="person_19684048">Rashi</persName>.
                        4: Fols. <locus from="168r" to="180v">168r-180v</locus>, probably a commentary by <persName key="person_59876084">Joseph Kara</persName>, or one based on it.
                        5: Fols. <locus from="206v" to="233v">206v-233v</locus>, a commentary probably by <persName key="person_59876084">Joseph Kara</persName>, but includes additions by <persName key="person_308257340">Solomon b. Samson</persName>.
                     </note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
